{"lemma":"رِواقٌ","slug":"رِواقٌ","root":"ر.#.ق","root_slug":"ر-_-ق","root_link":"/words/roots/ر-_-ق","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n17117","n17118","n17119"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B1%D9%90%D9%88%D8%A7%D9%82%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"drapery, curtain (of a tent)"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"colonnade, stoa, portico"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"pavilion (of an exposition)"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ri.waːq/","/ru.waːq/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n17117","headword_ar":"رَوَاقٌ","root":"rwq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see what next follows."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n17118","headword_ar":"رُوَاقٌ","root":"rwq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see what next follows."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n17119","headword_ar":"رِوَاقٌ","root":"rwq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, S, Mgh, O, Msb, K, &c.) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruwaAqN","text_ar":"رُوَاقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawaAqN","text_ar":"رَوَاقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bayot","text_ar":"بَيْت"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tent"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fusoTaAT","text_ar":"فُسْطَاط"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.], (Lth, JK, O, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"supported upon one pole in the middle thereof;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, O, Msb;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawoqN","text_ar":"رَوْقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K, * TA; expl. in the"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1192},{"kind":"text","text":"former as signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fusoTaAT","text_ar":"فُسْطَاط"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and its pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^arowaAqN","text_ar":"اَرْوَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is expl. in the S as signifying"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fasaATiyTu","text_ar":"فَسَاطِيطُ"},{"kind":"text","text":";) accord. to Lth: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a roof in the front,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fore part, of a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bayot","text_ar":"بَيْت"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tent"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (S, O, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawoqN","text_ar":"رَوْقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a curtain that is extended below the roof;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawoqN","text_ar":"رَوْقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; which latter is expl. in the K as signifying simply"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a curtain:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riwaAq","text_ar":"رِوَاق"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bayot","text_ar":"بَيْت"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or tent] is the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"curtain of the front,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fore part, thereof, extending from the top"},{"kind":"text","text":"thereof"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to the ground:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ, TA:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"piece of cloth such as is called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kisaA='","text_ar":"كِسَا=ء"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"let down upon the front,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fore part, of a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bayot","text_ar":"بَيْت"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from the top thereof to the ground:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawoqN","text_ar":"رَوْقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riwaAqN","text_ar":"رِوَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) and each signifies the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uq~ap","text_ar":"شُقَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"oblong piece of cloth"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is beneath the upper,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"uppermost,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uq~ap","text_ar":"شُقَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bayot","text_ar":"بَيْت"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or tent]: (Az, O, K:) or sometimes the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rwAq","text_ar":"رواق"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one such piece of cloth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and sometimes of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"two such pieces,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and sometimes of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"three:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and, (Msb,) or as some say, (Mgh, TA,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riwaAqN","text_ar":"رِوَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies (assumed tropical:)  the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"front,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fore part,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bayot","text_ar":"بَيْت"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or tent]; (Z, Mgh, Msb, TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawoqN","text_ar":"رَوْقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (JK, Z, K;) its hinder part being called its"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kifaA='","text_ar":"كِفَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":", and its two sides being called its"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAlifataAni","text_ar":"خَالِفَتَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) whence the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bayotihi","text_ar":"بَيْتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaEaduwA fiY rawoqi","text_ar":"قَعَدُوا فِى رَوْقِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riwaAqi bayotihi","text_ar":"رِوَاقِ بَيْتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e. (tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They sat in"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the front"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fore part"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of his tent"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (Z, TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawoqN","text_ar":"رَوْقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a tent;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Daraba rawoqahu","text_ar":"ضَرَبَ رَوْقَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He pitched his tent"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S:) and [hence] the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"place of the huntsman"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in which he conceals himself to lie in wait"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (K;) as being likened to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rwAq","text_ar":"رواق"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rwAq","text_ar":"رواق"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a place that affords shelter in rain:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(MA:) [and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a portico;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and particularly"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as surrounds the court of a mosque;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sud~apN","text_ar":"سُدَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":";) in some of the large collegiate mosques, as, for instance, in the mosque El-Azhar, in Cairo, divided into a number of distinct apartments for students of different provinces or countries, each of which apartments by itself is termed a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riwaAq","text_ar":"رِوَاق"},{"kind":"text","text":":] the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rwAq","text_ar":"رواق"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^arowiqapN","text_ar":"اَرْوِقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruwqN","text_ar":"رُوقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, O, Msb, K;) the former a pl. of pauc. and the latter of mult. (S, O.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alr~iwaAqu mina Als~aHaAbi","text_ar":"الرِّوَاقُ مِنَ السَّحَابِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", expl. in the TA as meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mA dAr minohu kariwaAqi Albayoti","text_ar":"ما دار مِنْهُ كَرِوَاقِ البَيْتِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": but"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dAr","text_ar":"دار"},{"kind":"text","text":"is here evidently a mistranscription for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaAna","text_ar":"كَانَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and the meaning is, (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The part, of the clouds, that resembles the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rwAq","text_ar":"رواق"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the tent."},{"kind":"text","text":"See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawoqu Als~aHaAbi","text_ar":"رَوْقُ السَّحَابِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", near the end of the paragraph commencing with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawoqN","text_ar":"رَوْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b3-  [Hence also,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riwaAqu All~ayoli","text_ar":"رِوَاقُ اللَّيْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The curtain of night:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the first part of night;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the greater,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"main, part thereof."},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISd, K. [It is implied in the latter that one says also in this instance and in the next"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruwaAq","text_ar":"رُوَاق"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) You say, of night,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mad~a riwaAqa Zulomatihi","text_ar":"مَدَّ رِوَاقَ ظُلْمَتِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It extended the curtain of its darkness"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, Msb:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aloqaY","text_ar":"اَلْقَى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^arowiqatahu","text_ar":"اَرْوِقَتَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It let fall its curtains"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.) [See also an ex. in a verse cited voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"murim~N","text_ar":"مُرِمٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rm","text_ar":"رم"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riwaAqu AlEayoni","text_ar":"رِوَاقُ العَيْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The eyebrow."},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK, K.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riwaAqu","text_ar":"رِوَاقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[imperfectly decl. as being a proper name and of the fem. gender, though it is implied in the K that it is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alr~iwaAqu","text_ar":"الرِّوَاقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alr~uwaAqu","text_ar":"الرُّوَاقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] is a name for"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The ewe,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K,) by which she is called to be milked, by the cry"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riwaAq riwaAq","text_ar":"رِوَاق رِوَاق"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (O;) but not unless she be ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawoqaA='","text_ar":"رَوْقَا=ء","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app., if not a mistranscription for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waroqaA='","text_ar":"وَرْقَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":", formed from this latter by transposition, and thus meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dusky:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^arowaqu","text_ar":"اَرْوَقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (O, K.)"}],"source_refs":["MA","K","Lth","JK","O","Msb","TA","S","AZ","Mgh","Az","Z"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}